Milonga Querida
01 Nov 2019, 06:52 by Redazione
Saturday 2nd November, starting at 10 pm, an evening dedicated to tango, organized by TangoQuerido, in via del Fante 84.
Possibility to book the shuttle service from the ferries following the directions on the Tango Querido Messina page.
